---
title: Double Sweet Chilli Beef Noodle Stir-Fry with Veggies & Sesame Seeds
description: Golden ropes of egg noodles are wrapping up all the flavours of sweet and savour in this vibrant stir-fry. Oyster sauce, sweet chilli and sweet soy seasoning enrobe tender beef strips and sauteed veggies for tonnes of flavour that’ll have you coming back for more.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
